        <span class="pl">( <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/mittermeier/reviews?cat_id=1002">2篇</a> )</span></h2>
        
        <div class="comment-item">
            <div class="pic">
                <a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/1471507/" title="Ocean&#39;s Thirteen"><img src="http://img5.douban.com/spic/s1798189.jpg" alt="Ocean&#39;s Thirteen"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>
                    <a title="几个有趣的细节" href="http://movie.douban.com/review/1212105/" class="title">几个有趣的细节</a>
                </h3>
                <div class="author">
                    <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/mittermeier/">米达麦亚</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;评论:&nbsp;<a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/1471507/">Ocean&#39;s Thirteen</a>
                </div>
                <p>1、麦特戴蒙穿着黑衣服在大街上打电话那一段场景，镜头摇晃的非常厉害。很明显是在恶搞《谍影重重》。
2、工人们罢工之后，罗汉们开的会议上，一伙人边吃饺子边讨论，而且用的是筷子。
3、麦特戴蒙假扮中国豪客随从，从飞机上走下来时，穿着黑色中山装，黑色皮鞋，却露出一截白袜子。不知是剧组的疏忽，还是在暗讽中国...<a href="http://movie.douban.com/review/1212105/">(49回应)</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="comment-item">
            <div class="pic">
                <a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/1578507/" title="The Bourne Ultimatum"><img src="http://img3.douban.com/spic/s2619292.jpg" alt="The Bourne Ultimatum"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>
                    <a title="Nicky和Bourne的关系" href="http://movie.douban.com/review/1208701/" class="title">Nicky和Bourne的关系</a>
                </h3>
                <div class="author">
                    <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/mittermeier/">米达麦亚</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;评论:&nbsp;<a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/1578507/">The Bourne Ultimatum</a>
                </div>
                <p>第三部有这么个镜头，两人在咖啡馆里，
Bourne问：“Why are you helping me?”
Nicky摆弄了半天杯子，低着头说：“It was difficult for, with you.”
两人无语了半天，Nicky一脸哀怨地问：“You really don&#39;t remember anything?”
Bourne说：“No”
Nicky顿时一脸失望。
从这里可以推测，Nicky在Bourne失忆之前...<a href="http://movie.douban.com/review/1208701/">(8回应)</a></p>
